=head1 NAME

WWW::Craigslist - Post free stuff on Craigslist.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This module is largely deprecated due to captchas added to craigslist,
and is mainly here for educational (positive or negative) purposes.

WWW::Craigslist is an API to Craigslist which allows you to post items
that you are giving away for free.

